item.description:
We're continuing in August with another of our famous Cashflow Meetups! ANY EXPERIENCE LEVEL IS WELCOME!! We always have some who have never played before as well as veterans. We will shoot for having a 202 board, but as always we reserve that board for those who have gotten out of the Rat Race at least five times.

THIS TIME, however, we will be doing something SPECIAL to shake it up a bit!!

There is parking on Hemenway Street. Even though it says Fenway Resident, I have never gotten a ticket there. If you have any trouble finding us, please feel free to call my cell (617-519-3163).

PLEASE BE ON TIME!!! We will start PROMPTLY at three.

We're looking forward to seeing you ALL there on Sunday August 16!

Russ
617-519-3163
item.name: REGULAR Cashflow Meetup
